---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Sip & Paint Pottery"
  description="Adult pottery painting with BYOB beverages in Centerville, TN. A sophisticated and fun evening experience for adults!"
  price="$20-30"
  duration="1.5-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="adult pottery painting, sip and paint pottery, BYOB pottery, adult craft night, pottery painting experience, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Sip & Paint Pottery - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Join us for Sip & Paint Pottery at Made @ The Local, an exclusive adult pottery painting experience where you can bring your favorite beverages and create beautiful ceramic art in a relaxed, social atmosphere. Perfect for date nights, girls' nights, or a sophisticated evening with friends.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Sip & Paint Pottery is designed specifically for adults who want to unwind, socialize, and create art in an elegant setting. Bring your favorite wine, beer, cocktails, or non-alcoholic beverages—we provide the atmosphere and creativity. Select from our curated collection of quality ceramic pieces, then paint with professional-grade ceramic paints while enjoying your drinks and great conversation. Whether you're painting intricate designs, abstract art, or decorative pieces, our experienced instructors are available to guide your artistic vision. After your painting session, we handle the professional glazing and kiln-firing, so you'll take home beautiful, finished pieces that are both art and functional pottery. It's an experience that combines creativity, relaxation, and socializing—a perfect escape from everyday life.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Premium ceramic pottery pieces to personalize</li>
      <li>Professional ceramic paints and complete color palette</li>
      <li>Quality brushes and painting supplies</li>
      <li>Expert guidance from experienced instructors</li>
      <li>Comfortable, relaxed adult-focused atmosphere</li>
      <li>BYOB beverage service (bring wine, beer, cocktails, or non-alcoholic drinks)</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Take home your finished pottery pieces</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Date nights and romantic evenings</li>
      <li>Girls' nights out or friend gatherings</li>
      <li>Adult craft experiences with beverages</li>
      <li>Team bonding and social events</li>
      <li>Bachelor and bachelorette celebrations</li>
      <li>Sophisticated alternative to typical evening activities</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Arrive and settle in with your beverages (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Select your ceramic pieces to paint (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint and create with instructor guidance (60-90 minutes)</li>
      <li>Final touches and details (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing (we handle the rest)</li>
      <li>Pick up your finished pieces in 2 weeks</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $20-30 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1.5-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome<br />
      <strong>Age Requirement:</strong> Adults 21+ for alcoholic beverages
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your Sip & Paint Pottery night!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033. Minimum group size: 4 people.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

